:markdown
  The ``info-icon`` block is used to display icons to hint at an informative
  text element.

  Use it together with the ``info-text`` block and the ``slide``
  plugin to create slide in and slide out information text blocks.

:sample
  .l-container
    .form
      .form__group
        .form__group__label
          .info-icon
            a(href='#').info-icon__icon
            label.info-icon__label Was wurde besch√§digt?
        .form__group__control
          input.control.control--input(type='text')
      .info-text
        .info-text__content
          p.
            Hallo Welt!
